article.description: — Luke Sutherland had 22 points in Le Moyne's 74-58 victory over Saint Francis (Pa.) on Saturday night.
article.headline: Sutherland puts up 22 in Le Moyne's 74-58 win over Saint Francis (PA)
article.linkText: Sutherland puts up 22 in Le Moyne's 74-58 win over Saint Francis (PA)
article.story: LORETTO, Pa. -- — Luke Sutherland had 22 points in Le Moyne's 74-58 victory over Saint Francis (Pa.) on Saturday night. Sutherland added seven rebounds and eight assists for the Dolphins (14-16, 9-7 Northeast Conference). Kaiyem Cleary added 16 points while going 4 of 8 from the floor, including 2 for 4 from 3-point range, and 6 for 6 from the line, and they also had six rebounds. Darrick Jones Jr. shot 3 for 3 from beyond the arc and 3 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with 12 points. The Red Flash (8-21, 3-13) were led by Carlos Lopez Jr., who recorded 17 points. Saint Francis also got 11 points and nine rebounds from Bobby Rosenberger III. In addition, Aaron Talbert had 10 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
